<lb n="0780b02" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 687</head>
<lb n="0780b03" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title><note n="0780008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【三】</note><note n="0780008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛說〕－【宋】<app><lem resp="CBETA.march">＊</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app>【元】<app><lem resp="CBETA.march">＊</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app>【明】<app><lem resp="CBETA.march">＊</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app></note><app n="0780008"><lem wit="【大】">佛說</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>孝子經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0780b04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0780b05" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0780009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（失譯…晉錄））＝失譯【宋】【元】，失譯人名【明】</note><note n="0780009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（（失譯…晉錄））＝失譯【宋】【元】，＝失譯人名【明】</note><app n="0780009" word-count="9"><lem wit="【大】">失譯<note n="0780010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人名〕－【宮】</note><app n="0780010"><lem wit="【大】">人名</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>今附西晉錄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">失譯</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">失譯人名</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0780b06" ed="T"/><div1 type="jing"><p id="pT16p0780b0601">佛問諸沙門：「親之生子，懷<note n="0780011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＝抱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">之＝抱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780011"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">抱</rdg></app>十月，身為重
<lb n="0780b07" ed="T"/>病。臨生之日，母危父怖，其情難言。既生之
<lb n="0780b08" ed="T"/>後推燥臥濕，精誠之至血化為乳，摩<note n="0780012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拭＝飾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">拭＝飾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780012"><lem wit="【大】">拭</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">飾</rdg></app>澡
<lb n="0780b09" ed="T"/>浴，衣食教詔，禮賂師友，<note n="0780013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">奉＝重【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">奉＝重【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780013"><lem wit="【大】">奉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">重</rdg></app>貢君長；子顏和
<lb n="0780b10" ed="T"/>悅親亦欣豫，子設慘<note n="0780014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慼＝戚【三】</note><note n="0780014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">慼＝戚【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0780014"><lem wit="【大】">慼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">戚</rdg></app>親心焦枯，<note n="0780015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（出門…之））八字＝入門存之出顧履履【宮】</note><app n="0780015" word-count="8"><lem wit="【大】">出門愛
<lb n="0780b11" ed="T"/>念入則存之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">入門存之出顧履履</rdg></app>，心懷惕惕懼其不<note n="0780016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善＝成【宮】</note><app n="0780016"><lem wit="【大】">善</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">成</rdg></app>。親恩若
<lb n="0780b12" ed="T"/><note n="0780017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＋（當）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">此＋（當）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780017"><lem wit="【大】">此</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">此當</rdg></app>，何以報<note n="0780018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔之〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔之〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780018"><lem wit="【大】">之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>？」</p><p id="pT16p0780b1206" place="inline">諸沙門對曰：「唯當盡禮慈心
<lb n="0780b13" ed="T"/>供養，以賽<note n="0780019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">親＝養【宮】</note><app n="0780019"><lem wit="【大】">親</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">養</rdg></app><note n="0780020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恩＋（耳）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">恩＋（耳）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780020"><lem wit="【大】">恩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">恩耳</rdg></app>。」</p><p id="pT16p0780b1307" place="inline">世尊又曰：「子之養親，甘露
<lb n="0780b14" ed="T"/>百味以<note n="0780021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恣＝咨【宮】</note><app n="0780021"><lem wit="【大】">恣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">咨</rdg></app>其口，天樂眾音以娛其耳，名衣
<lb n="0780b15" ed="T"/>上服光耀其<note n="0780022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">身＝體【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">身＝體【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780022"><lem wit="【大】">身</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">體</rdg></app>，兩肩荷負周流四海，訖子
<lb n="0780b16" ed="T"/>年命以賽<note n="0780023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">養恩＝恩養【三】</note><note n="0780023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">養恩＝恩養【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0780023"><lem wit="【大】">養恩</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">恩養</rdg></app>，可謂孝乎？」</p><p id="pT16p0780b1611" place="inline">諸沙門曰：「<note n="0780024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟＝唯【宮】</note><app n="0780024"><lem wit="【大】">惟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">唯</rdg></app>
<lb n="0780b17" ed="T"/>孝之大莫尚<note n="0780025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">乎＝干【宮】</note><app n="0780025"><lem wit="【大】">乎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">干</rdg></app>茲？」</p><p id="pT16p0780b1708" place="inline">世尊<note n="0780026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔告〕－【宮】</note><app n="0780026"><lem wit="【大】">告</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>曰：「未為孝矣！若
<lb n="0780b18" ed="T"/>親頑闇不奉三尊，兇虐殘戾，濫竊非<note n="0780027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">理婬&CB00105;＝物情染【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">理婬&CB00105;＝物情染【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780027"><lem wit="【大】">理，婬
<lb n="0780b19" ed="T"/>&CB00105;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">物情染</rdg></app>外色，偽辭非道，<note n="0780028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">酖愐＝耽醉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">酖愐＝耽醉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780028"><lem wit="【大】">酖愐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">耽醉</rdg></app>荒亂，違背正真兇
<lb n="0780b20" ed="T"/>&CB00859;若<note n="0780029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斯＝此【宮】</note><app n="0780029"><lem wit="【大】">斯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">此</rdg></app>，子當極諫以啟悟之。<note n="0780030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔若〕－【宮】</note><app n="0780030"><lem wit="【大】">若</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>猶瞢瞢未
<lb n="0780b21" ed="T"/>悟，即為<note n="0780031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">義化當＝開化【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">義化當＝開化【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780031"><lem wit="【大】">義化，當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">開化</rdg></app>牽<note n="0780032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">譬＝&CB13520;【宮】</note><app n="0780032"><lem wit="【大】">譬</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&CB13520;</rdg></app>引類，示王者之牢獄、
<lb n="0780b22" ed="T"/>諸囚之刑戮曰：『斯為不軌，身被眾毒，自招
<lb n="0780b23" ed="T"/>殞命。命終神去，繫于太山，湯火萬毒獨<note n="0780033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">呼＝喚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呼＝喚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780033"><lem wit="【大】">呼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">喚</rdg></app>
<lb n="0780b24" ed="T"/>無救。由彼履惡，遭<note n="0780034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斯＝此【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0780034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">斯＝此【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0780034"><lem wit="【大】">斯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">此</rdg></app>重殃<note n="0780035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">矣設＝若【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">矣設＝若【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780035"><lem wit="【大】">矣。』設</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">若</rdg></app>復未移，
<lb n="0780b25" ed="T"/><note n="0780036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吟＝悲【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">吟＝悲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780036"><lem wit="【大】">吟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">悲</rdg></app>泣啼<note n="0780037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嗷＝號【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780037" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嗷＝號【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780037"><lem wit="【大】">嗷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">號</rdg></app>絕<note n="0780038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＝無【宮】</note><app n="0780038"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">無</rdg></app>飲食，親雖不明，必以恩
<lb n="0780b26" ed="T"/>愛之痛懼子死矣。<note n="0780039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">猶＝由【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">猶＝由【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780039"><lem wit="【大】">猶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">由</rdg></app>當強忍伏心崇<note n="0780040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（正）＋道【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（正）＋道【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780040"><lem wit="【大】">道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">正道</rdg></app>，若
<lb n="0780b27" ed="T"/>親遷志奉佛五戒，仁<note n="0780041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惻＝測【明】，懼【宮】</note><note n="0780041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惻＝測【明】，＝懼【宮】</note><app n="0780041"><lem wit="【大】">惻</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">測</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">懼</rdg></app>不殺，清讓不盜，貞
<lb n="0780b28" ed="T"/>潔不婬，守信不欺，孝順不醉<note n="0780042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780042" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780042"><lem wit="【大】">者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>，宗門之內，
<lb n="0780b29" ed="T"/>即<note n="0780043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">親＋（父）【宮】</note><app n="0780043"><lem wit="【大】">親</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">親父</rdg></app>慈子孝，夫正婦貞，九族和睦僕使<note n="0780044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">順從＝恭順【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">順從＝恭順【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780044"><lem wit="【大】">順
<pb n="0780c" ed="T" id="T16.0687.0780c"/>
<lb n="0780c01" ed="T"/>從</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">恭順</rdg></app>，潤澤遠被含血受恩，十方諸佛天龍鬼神，
<lb n="0780c02" ed="T"/>有道之君、忠平之臣，黎庶萬姓無不敬愛，祐
<lb n="0780c03" ed="T"/>而安之。<note n="0780045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">數＝雖【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">數＝雖【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780045"><lem wit="【大】">數</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雖</rdg></app>有顛倒之政，&CB02439;<note n="0780046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嬖＝&CB00858;【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嬖＝&CB00858;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780046"><lem wit="【大】">嬖</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&CB00858;</rdg></app>之輔，兇兒妖
<lb n="0780c04" ed="T"/>婦，千邪萬怪，無如已何。<note n="0780047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">於＝如【宮】</note><app n="0780047"><lem wit="【大】">於</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">如</rdg></app>是二親處世常
<lb n="0780c05" ed="T"/>安，壽終魂靈<note n="0780048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">往＝昇【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">往＝昇【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780048"><lem wit="【大】">往</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">昇</rdg></app>生天上，諸佛共會得聞法
<lb n="0780c06" ed="T"/>言，獲道度世長與苦別。」</p>
<lb n="0780c07" ed="T"/><p id="pT16p0780c0701">佛告諸沙門：「&CB00418;世無孝唯斯為孝耳。能令<note n="0780049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（二）＋親【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（二）＋親【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780049"><lem wit="【大】">親</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">二親</rdg></app>
<lb n="0780c08" ed="T"/>去惡為善，奉持五戒，執三<note n="0780050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＝貞【宮】</note><app n="0780050"><lem wit="【大】">自</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">貞</rdg></app>歸，朝奉而暮
<lb n="0780c09" ed="T"/>終者，恩重於親乳哺之養無量之惠。若不能
<lb n="0780c10" ed="T"/>以三尊之至化其親者，雖為<note n="0780051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">孝＝前【宮】</note><app n="0780051"><lem wit="【大】">孝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">前</rdg></app>養<note n="0780052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">猶＝由【宮】</note><app n="0780052"><lem wit="【大】">猶</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">由</rdg></app><note n="0780053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">為不孝＝不孝矣【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">為不孝＝不孝矣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780053"><lem wit="【大】">為不
<lb n="0780c11" ed="T"/>孝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">不孝矣</rdg></app>。無以&CB00858;妻遠賢不親，女情多欲好色無倦，
<lb n="0780c12" ed="T"/>違孝<note n="0780054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">殺＝敬【宮】</note><app n="0780054"><lem wit="【大】">殺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">敬</rdg></app>親，國政荒亂，萬民流<note n="0780055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">亡＝忘【宮】</note><app n="0780055"><lem wit="【大】">亡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">忘</rdg></app>，本志惠
<lb n="0780c13" ed="T"/>施，<note n="0780056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">禮＝以【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780056" resp="CBETA" type="mod">禮＝以【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780056"><lem wit="【大】">禮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">以</rdg></app><note n="0780057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">式＝戒【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780057"><lem wit="【大】">式</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】【宮】">戒</rdg></app>自<note n="0780058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">撿＝檢【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780058"><lem wit="【大】">撿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】【宮】">檢</rdg></app>，<note n="0780059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔軟〕－【宮】</note><app n="0780059"><lem wit="【大】">軟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>心<app><lem resp="CBETA.maha" cf1="KI20n0827_p1143b23" wit="【CBETA】【麗】">崇</lem><rdg wit="【大】">祟</rdg></app>仁，<note n="0780060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">烝烝＝蒸蒸【三】，拯【宮】</note><note n="0780060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">烝烝＝蒸蒸【宋】【元】【明】，＝拯【宮】</note><app n="0780060"><lem wit="【大】">烝烝</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">蒸蒸</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">拯</rdg></app>進德，潛
<lb n="0780c14" ed="T"/>意寂寞，學志叡達，名<note n="0780061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">動＝勳【宮】</note><app n="0780061"><lem wit="【大】">動</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">勳</rdg></app>諸天，明齊賢者，自
<lb n="0780c15" ed="T"/>穢妻聚，惑志女色，荒迷<note n="0780062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">于＝子【宮】</note><app n="0780062"><lem wit="【大】">于</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">子</rdg></app>欲，妖<note n="0780063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蠱姿態＝治恣能【宮】</note><app n="0780063"><lem wit="【大】">蠱姿態</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">治恣能</rdg></app>其
<lb n="0780c16" ed="T"/>變萬端。薄智之夫、淺見之士，&CB00418;其如此，不
<lb n="0780c17" ed="T"/><note n="0780064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">覺＝學【宮】</note><app n="0780064"><lem wit="【大】">覺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">學</rdg></app>微漸，遂迴志沒身，從彼<note n="0780065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">魃魅＝妖媚【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780065" resp="CBETA" type="mod">魃魅＝妖媚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780065"><lem wit="【大】">魃魅</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">妖媚</rdg></app>邪巧之<note n="0780066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">亂＝辭【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780066" resp="CBETA" type="mod">亂＝辭【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780066"><lem wit="【大】">亂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">辭</rdg></app>，
<lb n="0780c18" ed="T"/>或危親殺君，<note n="0780067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00385;＝悟【宮】</note><app n="0780067"><lem wit="【大】">&CB00385;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">悟</rdg></app>色情蕩，忿<note n="0780068" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嫉＝戾【宮】</note><app n="0780068"><lem wit="【大】">嫉</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">戾</rdg></app>怠慢，散心盲
<lb n="0780c19" ed="T"/><note n="0780069" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">冥＝瞑【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780069" resp="CBETA" type="mod">冥＝瞑【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780069"><lem wit="【大】">冥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">瞑</rdg></app>，等行鳥獸，自古世來，無不由之<note n="0780070" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">殺＝亡【三】【宮】</note><note n="0780070" resp="CBETA" type="mod">殺＝亡【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0780070"><lem wit="【大】">殺</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">亡</rdg></app>身滅
<pb n="0781a" ed="T" id="T16.0687.0781a"/>
<lb n="0781a01" ed="T"/>宗，是以沙門獨而不雙，清潔其志<note n="0781001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝唯【三】【宮】</note><note n="0781001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝唯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781001"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">唯</rdg></app>道是
<lb n="0781a02" ed="T"/>務。奉<app type="＊" source="0780034"><lem wit="【大】">斯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">此</rdg></app>明<note n="0781002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">戒＝教【宮】</note><app n="0781002"><lem wit="【大】">戒</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">教</rdg></app>，為君即保四海，為臣即忠，
<lb n="0781a03" ed="T"/>以仁養民，<note n="0781003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔即〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0781003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔即〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781003"><lem wit="【大】">即</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">&lac;</rdg></app>父法明子孝慈，夫信婦貞。優
<lb n="0781a04" ed="T"/>婆塞、優婆夷執行如<note n="0781004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝此【三】【宮】</note><note n="0781004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">是＝此【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781004"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">此</rdg></app>，世世逢佛見法得道。」</p>
<lb n="0781a05" ed="T"/><p id="pT16p0781a0501">佛說如是，弟子歡喜。</p></div1>
